                                <i class="fa-solid fa-location-crosshairs"></i><span class="fw-semibold mx-2">Notice Period:</span> <span> @(employeedetail == null ? "" : employeedetail.NoticePeriod == null ? "" : employeedetail.NoticePeriod) </span>
